            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EYour%20spiritual%20inheritance%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20you%20possess.%20The%20daughters%20of%20Zelophehad%20knew%20that%20and%20thus%20demanded%20their%20inheritance%20(Numbers%2027%3A4).%20They%20refused%20to%20let%20any%20factor%20stand%20in%20their%20way%20of%20possessing%20what%20their%20father%20had%20left%20to%20them%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20God%20honored%20their%20faith.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYour%20spiritual%20inheritance%20may%20be%20the%20transfer%20of%20someone%20else's%20anointing%20to%20you%20before%20that%20person's%20death.%20Moses%20transferred%20his%20anointing%20to%20Joshua%20by%20the%20laying%20on%20of%20hands%20(Numbers%2027%3A23).%20Jesus%20received%20His%20inheritance%20when%20He%20went%20into%20the%20Jordan%20and%20was%20baptized%20by%20John%20(Luke%203%3A21-22).%20Elisha%20appropriated%20his%20inheritance%20when%20he%20saw%20Elijah%20go%20up%20in%20a%20whirlwind%20and%20drop%20his%20mantle%20from%20the%20chariot%20(2%20Kings%202%3A11-13).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20has%20given%20you%20a%20mantle%20of%20inheritance-some%20ministry%2C%20some%20mission%2C%20some%20calling-that%20belongs%20to%20you%20alone.%20Will%20you%20be%20like%20Esau%20who%20despised%20his%20inheritance%20and%20birthright%20and%20sold%20it%20all%20for%20a%20little%20bowl%20of%20soup%3F%20Never%20forfeit%20or%20throw%20your%20heritage%20away%20as%20though%20it%20were%20worthless.%20Instead%2C%20seize%20it%2C%20claim%20it%2C%20and%20believe%20that%20God%20will%20use%20it%20to%20glorify%20His%20name.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Numbers.26:52-28:15",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENumbers%2026%3A52-28%3A15%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_52%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2252%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E52%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_53%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2253%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E53%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BDivide%20the%20land%20among%20the%20tribes%2C%20and%20distribute%20the%20grants%20of%20land%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20tribes%26%23x2019%3B%20populations%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20the%20number%20of%20names%20on%20the%20list.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_54%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2254%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E54%3C%2Fspan%3EGive%20the%20larger%20tribes%20more%20land%20and%20the%20smaller%20tribes%20less%20land%2C%20each%20group%20receiving%20a%20grant%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20size%20of%20its%20population.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_55%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2255%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E55%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20must%20assign%20the%20land%20by%20lot%2C%20and%20give%20land%20to%20each%20ancestral%20tribe%20according%20to%20the%20number%20of%20names%20on%20the%20list.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_56%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2256%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E56%3C%2Fspan%3EEach%20grant%20of%20land%20must%20be%20assigned%20by%20lot%20among%20the%20larger%20and%20smaller%20tribal%20groups.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_57%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2257%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Tribe%20of%20Levi%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E57%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Levites%20who%20were%20counted%20according%20to%20their%20clans%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3EThe%20Gershonite%20clan%2C%20named%20after%20their%20ancestor%20Gershon.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3EThe%20Kohathite%20clan%2C%20named%20after%20their%20ancestor%20Kohath.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3EThe%20Merarite%20clan%2C%20named%20after%20their%20ancestor%20Merari.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_58%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2258%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E58%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Libnites%2C%20the%20Hebronites%2C%20the%20Mahlites%2C%20the%20Mushites%2C%20and%20the%20Korahites%20were%20all%20subclans%20of%20the%20Levites.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3ENow%20Kohath%20was%20the%20ancestor%20of%20Amram%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_59%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2259%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E59%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20Amram%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wife%20was%20named%20Jochebed.%20She%20also%20was%20a%20descendant%20of%20Levi%2C%20born%20among%20the%20Levites%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt.%20Amram%20and%20Jochebed%20became%20the%20parents%20of%20Aaron%2C%20Moses%2C%20and%20their%20sister%2C%20Miriam.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_60%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2260%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E60%3C%2Fspan%3ETo%20Aaron%20were%20born%20Nadab%2C%20Abihu%2C%20Eleazar%2C%20and%20Ithamar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_61%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2261%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E61%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Nadab%20and%20Abihu%20died%20when%20they%20burned%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20wrong%20kind%20of%20fire%2C%20different%20than%20he%20had%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_62%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2262%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E62%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20men%20from%20the%20Levite%20clans%20who%20were%20one%20month%20old%20or%20older%20numbered%2023%2C000.%20But%20the%20Levites%20were%20not%20included%20in%20the%20registration%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20because%20they%20were%20not%20given%20an%20allotment%20of%20land%20when%20it%20was%20divided%20among%20the%20Israelites.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_63%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2263%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E63%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20these%20are%20the%20results%20of%20the%20registration%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20as%20conducted%20by%20Moses%20and%20Eleazar%20the%20priest%20on%20the%20plains%20of%20Moab%20beside%20the%20Jordan%20River%2C%20across%20from%20Jericho.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_64%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2264%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E64%3C%2Fspan%3ENot%20one%20person%20on%20this%20list%20had%20been%20among%20those%20listed%20in%20the%20previous%20registration%20taken%20by%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%20in%20the%20wilderness%20of%20Sinai.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_26_65%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2226%22%20vn%3D%2265%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E65%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20said%20of%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThey%20will%20all%20die%20in%20the%20wilderness.%26%23x201D%3B%20Not%20one%20of%20them%20survived%20except%20Caleb%20son%20of%20Jephunneh%20and%20Joshua%20son%20of%20Nun.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_1%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENumbers%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Daughters%20of%20Zelophehad%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20a%20petition%20was%20presented%20by%20the%20daughters%20of%20Zelophehad%26%23x2014%3BMahlah%2C%20Noah%2C%20Hoglah%2C%20Milcah%2C%20and%20Tirzah.%20Their%20father%2C%20Zelophehad%2C%20was%20a%20descendant%20of%20Hepher%20son%20of%20Gilead%2C%20son%20of%20Makir%2C%20son%20of%20Manasseh%2C%20son%20of%20Joseph.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_2%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20women%20stood%20before%20Moses%2C%20Eleazar%20the%20priest%2C%20the%20tribal%20leaders%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20community%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E27%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Tent%20of%20Meeting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_3%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BOur%20father%20died%20in%20the%20wilderness%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20said.%20%26%23x201C%3BHe%20was%20not%20among%20Korah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20followers%2C%20who%20rebelled%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20he%20died%20because%20of%20his%20own%20sin.%20But%20he%20had%20no%20sons.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_4%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhy%20should%20the%20name%20of%20our%20father%20disappear%20from%20his%20clan%20just%20because%20he%20had%20no%20sons%3F%20Give%20us%20property%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20relatives.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_5%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Moses%20brought%20their%20case%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_6%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20replied%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_7%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20claim%20of%20the%20daughters%20of%20Zelophehad%20is%20legitimate.%20You%20must%20give%20them%20a%20grant%20of%20land%20along%20with%20their%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20relatives.%20Assign%20them%20the%20property%20that%20would%20have%20been%20given%20to%20their%20father.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_8%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20give%20the%20following%20instructions%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%3A%20If%20a%20man%20dies%20and%20has%20no%20son%2C%20then%20give%20his%20inheritance%20to%20his%20daughters.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_9%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20if%20he%20has%20no%20daughter%20either%2C%20transfer%20his%20inheritance%20to%20his%20brothers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_10%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20he%20has%20no%20brothers%2C%20give%20his%20inheritance%20to%20his%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20brothers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_11%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20if%20his%20father%20has%20no%20brothers%2C%20give%20his%20inheritance%20to%20the%20nearest%20relative%20in%20his%20clan.%20This%20is%20a%20legal%20requirement%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20commanded%20Moses.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_12%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJoshua%20Chosen%20to%20Lead%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BClimb%20one%20of%20the%20mountains%20east%20of%20the%20river%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E27%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20mountains%20of%20Abarim.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20look%20out%20over%20the%20land%20I%20have%20given%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_13%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20you%20have%20seen%20it%2C%20you%20will%20die%20like%20your%20brother%2C%20Aaron%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_27_14%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2227%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Efor%20you%20both%20rebelled%20against%20my%20instructions%20in%20the%20wilderness%20of%20Zin.%20When%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20rebelled%2C%20you%20failed%20to%20demonstrate%20my%20holiness%20to%20them%20at%20the%20waters.%26%23x201D%3B%20(These%20are%20the%20waters%20of%20Meribah%20at%20Kadesh%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E27%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3